Author: BACON
Vol / Page: 184
Edition:
Quote: <i>Sole Charge </i>-The affectionate term applied to a country school having one teacher only. Maximum number of pupils for such a school is usually thirty five; after the role reaches this number, an assistant is appointed, making the school `a two teacher job'
